Maintainr - A lazy developer utility
===============================================================================

Maintainr is an utility designed to easily maintain small projects and spread
news about them.
Permits to collect todos, and share spare time among them accordly a
not-so-randomic heuristic.

Maintainr homepage is available at: http://madbob.org/Maintainr

REQUIREMENTS
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Maintainr depends on:

  - libgtk3 >= 3.1
  - libxml-2.0 >= 2.7.7

INSTALLATION
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
./configure
make
sudo make install

